          <h1 id="introduction">Introduction</h1>

<p>LINE BCRM tracks and understands your followers in Official Account, and gives you insights and tools to convert audiences into real customers.</p>

<p>LINE BCRM provides a variety of features to engage and convert your users, and improves retention for existing customers</p>

<p><strong><a href="#campaigns">Targeted and personalised messaging</a></strong><br>
Send targeted messages to groups, segments or individual users. Improve your CTR and engagement rates 100 folds by sending out personalised and engaging messages to individuals.</p>

<p><strong><a href="#link-campaigns">Track, analyze user behaviors and demographics</a></strong><br>
Measure the real interests of your users by tracking individual users&rsquo; clicks and interactions on Official Account Messages, as well as your e-commerce websites. Customizable surveys can also understand customer demographics and interests.</p>

<p><strong><a href="#user-messages">Always ON AIR</a></strong><br>
Listen to your customers - always receiving messages from your users, and receive insights on customer&rsquo;s needs and sentiments. Surprise guaranteed when you discover what your users are saying.</p>

<p><strong><a href="#one-on-one-chats">One-on-one chats</a></strong><br>
Chat and support your users one on one. Especially useful for Products with high Customer Lifetime Value. Improve your conversion and retention rate.</p>

